name: out_of_memory_metric
command: sudo /bin/bash /opt/yodlee_sensu_scripts/check_logs.sh -r 'Out of memory' -l /var/log/messages -t 30 > /dev/null; resp=$?; echo "$(echo -n $(hostname -f). | tac -s '.')check.out_of_memory $resp $(date +%s)"

name: check_nova_message_consumer
command: sudo /opt/sensu/embedded/bin/check-tail.rb --file /var/log/nova/nova-compute.log --lines 10 -P 'Failed to consume message from queue'
